2 Formulation The complete process of ChatGE framework can be seen as a multi-turn human-LLM interaction,Game Development as Human-LLM Interaction
 We first formulate the multi-turn Human-LLM in- teraction and then extend this concept to ChatGE,Game Development as Human-LLM Interaction
" In a multi-turn Human-LLM interaction, both the user input and the LLM’s output may be related to the interaction history, such as references to prior content",Game Development as Human-LLM Interaction
" The interaction history ht at turn t can be simply defined as: ht = ( ∅ if t = 0 {(iτ , oτ ) | τ = 1, 2, ",Game Development as Human-LLM Interaction
 ,Game Development as Human-LLM Interaction
