 7 Conclusion This paper introduces the Chat Game Engine (ChatGE) and proposes a paradigm for training ChatGE to allows users to develop custom games interactively using natural language,Game Development as Human-LLM Interaction
" To enable an LLM to function as a ChatGE, we instruct it to generate script segments, code snippets and inter- actions for each turn in the development process",Game Development as Human-LLM Interaction
" To facilitate the training process, a data synthesis",Game Development as Human-LLM Interaction
"pipeline is proposed to generate sufficient training data, as well as a three-stage progressive training strategy to enhance the joint capability of interac- tion and programming of the LLM",Game Development as Human-LLM Interaction
" Embodied in a poker game, we demonstrate the performance of the ChatGE through a comprehensive evaluation",Game Development as Human-LLM Interaction
" Limitations While our ChatGE offers exciting potential for ap- plying LLMs as multi-turn game development, sev- eral limitations warrant further exploration: (1) Limited scalability: We notice that it is still very hard to generalize ChatGE to all games or all game engines",Game Development as Human-LLM Interaction
" Instead, in this work, we choose a spe- cific game to illustrate the idea of ChatGE",Game Development as Human-LLM Interaction
 The entire data generation and training process must be repeated to adapt this approach to a new game,Game Development as Human-LLM Interaction
" However, all the prompts we use are designed to be game-agnostic, making them easily adaptable for use in other games",Game Development as Human-LLM Interaction
" Of course, our future work will definitely focuses on the scalability of ChatGE",Game Development as Human-LLM Interaction
 (2) Limited scope and modalities: Our current ChatGE primarily support text-based games like Poker,Game Development as Human-LLM Interaction
" Ad- ditional modalities such as images, sound, or video could enrich the game and are almost essential in modern video games, but this expansion presents technical and design challenges",Game Development as Human-LLM Interaction
 These limitations highlight the importance of ongoing research and development efforts aimed at addressing the chal- lenges associated with LLM-based game develop- ment,Game Development as Human-LLM Interaction
